data.description: Calling all first-time homebuyers and investors....This cozy, affordable 2 bed, 1 bath and 1 car ranch would look great with you in it or as part of your real estate portfolio. New furnace and AC, partially fenced yard. Partially finished basement with bonus room. And just minutes to downtown and the Med Center.
